# Because this chart is a test harness nested inside the teleport-util-lib
# library chart and it pulls the library's named templates in through a symlink
# (charts/teleport-util-lib -> ../../ — the lib chart directory), we have to
# ignore this dir in this root (application) chart to break the symlink loop
# Helm's loader would otherwise hit while walking the chart directory: the
# symlink points back into a directory that contains this chart (whose charts/
# symlinks back again), so the walk would never terminate. It's a filesystem
# traversal loop, not a dependency-graph cycle.
#
# One alternative would be `repository: file://../` in the dependency in
# Chart.yaml, but because helm-janitor doesn't run `helm dependency build`
# that isn't an option.
#
# NOTE: any other chart that symlinks this lib needs the same line in its own
# .helmignore (e.g. teleport-cluster/.helmignore), for the same reason.
test-chart/
